text: Svetlana Tarasevich (born 14 August 1979) is a Belarusian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Grodno
